RelevantChangelogs.Description: Updates endpoint to include new gatewayJ1939EngineSeconds stat type.
RelevantChangelogs.Details: Adds gatewayJ1939EngineSeconds to surface manual engine second readings when using a J1939/CAT cable that supports obd readings. This allows customers to fetch engine seconds that match engine hour readings on cloud.samsara.com.
